      },
      {
        "comment": "",
        "key": "屏幕共享已连接",
        "location": {
          "startingColumn": 40,
          "startingLine": 18
        }
      },
      {
        "comment": "",
        "key": "开启 AI 屏幕共享",
        "location": {
          "startingColumn": 66,
          "startingLine": 18
        }
      },
      {
        "comment": "",
        "key": "现在可以离开专注守望，AI 会在屏幕广播期间继续评估画面。",
        "location": {
          "startingColumn": 28,
          "startingLine": 21
        }
      },
      {
        "comment": "",
        "key": "请点下面的系统广播按钮，再在系统窗口中点“开始广播”。",
        "location": {
          "startingColumn": 28,
          "startingLine": 22
        }
      },
      {
        "comment": "",
        "key": "系统列表出现后，请选择“专注守望屏幕分析”。",
        "location": {
          "startingColumn": 30,
          "startingLine": 39
        }
      },
      {
        "comment": "",
        "key": "点上方“授权屏幕共享”按钮",
        "location": {
          "startingColumn": 57,
          "startingLine": 46
        }
      },
      {
        "comment": "",
        "key": "在系统窗口中确认“专注守望屏幕分析”",
        "location": {
          "startingColumn": 57,
          "startingLine": 47
        }
      },
      {
        "comment": "",
